title: 'There’s something bigger going on': State election chiefs rebuff Trump bid to seize voter rolls
description: Roughly two dozen states have rejected the Trump administration’s request, prompting an unprecedented legal clash between the Justice Department and state election officials.
content: Roughly two dozen states have rejected the Trump administration’s request, prompting an unprecedented legal clash between the Justice Department and state election officials.
